'''''Survivors''''', ni filime ya documentaire ya [[Siyera Lewone|Siyera Lewone yo muri]] 2018 - iyobowe na Banker White, Anna Fitch<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt7512950/</ref>, [[Lansana Mansaray]], na Arthur Pratt.  Iyi filime yakozwe n'abayobozi bane ubwabo hamwe na Sara Dosa, Samantha Grant, Justine Nagan, na Chris White<ref>https://www.globalhealthfilm.org/resources/25-survivors-2018</ref>.  Iyi filime ikurikira icyorezo cya Ebola gikwirakwira muri [[Siyera Lewone|Siyera]] Lewone cyanduye abantu 8.704 ikica 3.589 n'uburyo intwari za [[Siyera Lewone|Siyera]] Lewone zirandura iki cyorezo.<ref>https://www.amdoc.org/watch/survivors/</ref><ref>https://www.gavi.org/vaccineswork/book-club/review-survivors-hope-and-resilience-time-ebola</ref> 

Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://www.tfiny.org/films/detail/survivors</ref>. Iyi filime yatorewe kuba Emmy's Best Social Issue Documentaire mu 2018, ibaye filime ya mbere yo muri [[Afurika]] y'Iburengerazuba yakiriye igihembo.<ref>https://www.mirabelpictures.org/stories/2019/4/9/weowntvs-survivors-documentary-earns-nomination-for-2019-peabody-awards-1</ref><ref>https://wheatonwire.com/2019/survivors-documentary-screening/</ref> 

